"түзету үшін пайдалануға болады."

#. (itstool) path: sect1/para
#: C/genius.xml:468
msgid ""
"To run a program from a file, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Load and Run...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will run the "
